
Ranger Help for: enemy deer
===========================

SUMMARY:
Choosing deer means your Ranger is skilled at hunting deer, elk, stags,
and other antlered woodland or plains creatures.

This is a traditional tracker choice. It fits Rangers who want their enemy
species to reflect patient pursuit, spoor reading, and clean fieldcraft.

COMMAND:
  setenemy deer

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
